data.description: Discover comfort and convenience in this one-story, 3-bedroom, 2-full bath home in Monroe. Step into the welcoming foyer leading to a spacious living room, a charming breakfast area, and a practical utility room. Enjoy the warmth of a fireplace in the living space, creating a cozy ambiance. The kitchen is well-equipped with a dishwasher and electric range/oven, combining functionality with modern amenities. Retreat to the master's bedroom, featuring a walk-in closet and enhanced comfort with a ceiling fan. Outside, the covered porch and patio offer delightful spaces to relax, surrounded by wooden fencing for added privacy. This Monroe home is a perfect blend of style and practicality, providing a comfortable living experience.
